    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless, showcasing a deep, mirror-like finish with no scratches, dents, or stone chips of any kind. Inside, the leather interior is pristine, with no signs of wear, creases, or fading, and it still retains that new-car scent. Every mechanical component has been meticulously maintained, with a complete service history from the dealership. All features, including the electronics and climate control, function perfectly. This is a rare find for a collector or an enthusiast seeking a vehicle in museum-quality condition.",
