    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. It would best serve as a project car or a source for parts. The exterior shows significant wear, including heavy oxidation on the paint, visible rust on the rocker panels, and a prominent dent on the rear passenger side. Inside, the cabin requires extensive work; the upholstery is heavily torn, the headliner is sagging, and several interior trim pieces are missing or broken. Mechanically, while the engine does start, it idles roughly and the transmission shifts harshly. The tires are near the end of their life, and the brakes will need immediate replacement. This is a high-effort restoration project for someone with the right tools and time.",
