      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. If you\u2019re looking for a dependable car that\u2019s ready for your next adventure, this is the one! I\u2019ve kept it well-maintained, so it\u2019s all set for a new owner to jump in and go. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 32000.0,
