    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound 2008 Porsche Cayman S, powered by the 3.4L M97 flat-six engine featuring VarioCam Plus. This chassis excels in cornering kinematics due to its mid-engine configuration and optimized roll centers. The 6-speed manual transaxle provides crisp gear engagement, while the hydraulic power steering offers the tactile feedback modern EPAS systems lack. Maintained with technical rigor, the cooling system and suspension bushings have been recently serviced to ensure peak lateral acceleration performance. A well-sorted example with a healthy power-to-weight ratio, ready for the apex.",
      "price": 34800.0,
